PrecisAcceptance of the transfer from the Province of NEWFOUNDLAND of three parcels of land (1.1378 ha) situated at LOON BAY, Comfort Cove, for telecommunication purposes; (b) transfer to the Province of Newfoundland of a parcel of land (36 m²); and (c) authority to transfer the management, charge and direction of land acquired from the Department of Public Works to the Department of Transport.
